        Construct a spline. Note that the x axis is the direction the robot is facing if the start angle is 0
        Parameters:
        vCruise - - max velocity
        aMax - - max acceleration
        startVelocity - - the starting velocity of the Path
        endVelocity - - the ending velocity of the Path
        isBackwards - - if the robot will be moving backwards, make this true
        knots - - the points you want the robot to drive through
